{{Reflist|group=2}} == See Also == * {{ill|Yuka Shrine Main|ja|由加神社本宮|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Kumano Shrine (Kurashiki)|ja|熊野神社 (倉敷市林)|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Yoshida Yoshi-dō|ja|柴田義董|12=draft|12=draft}} – credited with painting the 50‐faced barrier paintings at Rendaiji. == External Links == * {{Commonscat|Rendaiji}} * [https://yugasan.jp/ Yugasan Rendaiji Official Website] * [https://www.city.kurashiki.okayama.jp/bunkahogo/ Kurashiki City Cultural Properties Protection Division] {{Normdaten}}
